5.0 of 5 bubbles
a must see
Apr 2015 • Couples
The collection of Cham artifacts here is huge, and interesting. Set in a a French colonial building, it really is a must see in Da Nang. Give yourself a couple of hours, there is a lot to take in. Occasional Cham dancing too if you like that kind of thing.
When you're done, go to the small pagoda next door, their are some amazing, unusual wooden deities, unpainted - just natural wood.
