A Great Collection of Cham Artifacts
Jun 2013 • Family
The Cham Museum (Bao Tang) is located in a busy street in Da Nang. I visited this museum on a couple of times as a side trip enroute to Hoi An from Hue City. There is a small entrance fee to get inside the museum. Most of the relics on display are archeological finds from the My Son Sanctuary. For a better understanding and appreciation of Cham culture a short trip to My Son Sanctuary is highly recommended.
