Well organised
May 2012 • Couples
Cham Museum, entrance fee 30,000 each. You can hire a guide to take you through it. We opted not to as every statue has a sign telling you where the piece came from and what it was about and a bit of history about which Cham region it came from.
Interesting, allow yourself at least 1 hour.
